Configurar WIFI portal Cautivo
------------------------------

apt-get install dpkg-dev debhelper libtool libssl-dev libcurl4-openssl-dev
wget -P /tmp 'http://ap.coova.org/chilli/coova-chilli-1.2.8.tar.gz'

########################################################################
wget -c "http://www.chillispot.org/download/chillispot_1.0_i386.deb"
apt-get install apache2 apache2.2-common apache2-mpm-worker apache2-utils





